    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098820/extras/34fd31d598fe8d456998c739c575f346.avif?t=1763672415\" width=596 height=133 /></span><br><br><strong>Rune Legacy Idle</strong> is a <i>role-playing game with idle mechanics</i> set in a classic high-fantasy world. Battle mythical monsters, train various skills, and challenge your friends to duels. Alternatively, team up with them for epic adventures. Enjoy an idle RPG experience where your journey never stops, even when you're away. Start your journey and craft your legend.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098820/extras/0945eabbc4e4b56a41fea14fc2fe92b8.webp?t=1763672415\" width=596 height=26 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098820/extras/a7d93880dc2b3b6da6044818a0309940.webp?t=1763672415\" width=600 height=60 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098820/extras/4d65d45fe3457c4448accc2859844653.poster.avif?t=1763672415\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098820/extras/4d65d45fe3457c4448accc2859844653.webm?t=1763672415\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098820/extras/4d65d45fe3457c4448accc2859844653.mp4?t=1763672415\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Create your own hero</strong> and customize them to your liking. Tailor your hero's abilities to match your gameplay style, whether as a powerful warrior, a cunning rogue, or a skilled mage. Train your hero in specific disciplines, and enhance their strengths. Enjoy a game where your personalized hero evolves and grows, reflecting your strategic choices and playstyle throughout the adventure.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098820/extras/0945eabbc4e4b56a41fea14fc2fe92b8.webp?t=1763672415\" width=596 height=26 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098820/extras/7c5d3566d27b6fc3559786c8e1ac882c.webp?t=1763672415\" width=600 height=60 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098820/extras/325d8d10547a5a9437042fe8d625ffa3.poster.avif?t=1763672415\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098820/extras/325d8d10547a5a9437042fe8d625ffa3.webm?t=1763672415\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098820/extras/325d8d10547a5a9437042fe8d625ffa3.mp4?t=1763672415\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Gather resources and craft</strong>. Chop wood in lush forests, mine precious ores, or fish in serene waters. Use these resources to craft powerful weapons and armours. Whether forging legendary armor or preparing delicious meals, Rune Legacy Idle offers countless opportunities to master your craft and thrive.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098820/extras/0945eabbc4e4b56a41fea14fc2fe92b8.webp?t=1763672415\" width=596 height=26 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098820/extras/6f3e70aea6b62b42d09792e2dfa85cba.webp?t=1763672415\" width=600 height=60 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><v